## Introduction

This is a Markdown file with a few Octave code chunks.

## Hello World

```{oc wait=500}
disp("Hello Octave World!")
```

## Variable Values

```{oc}
x=1
disp(x)
```

In the next code chunk we increment x:

```{oc}
x=x+1
disp(x)
```

## Inline code evaluation

The value of x is `oc disp(x)`!

